{
  "id": "adv_card_kan_51_02",
  "title": "kana",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "あー……せっかくのオフなのにkanaのプレゼントを\n選んでるなんて、何やってるのかしら、私……",
      "startTime": 4.7529847062,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.8333330791
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "まさしく、時間の無駄よね\nせめて時給が発生してもいいと思うんだけど……",
      "startTime": 11.7,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3599.998601300001,
          "startTime": 15.2999986013
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……",
      "startTime": 16.8666680654,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.3000015259
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "うわっ、びっくりした。辛気臭いため息が\n聞こえると思ったら、mihoじゃない",
      "startTime": 22.0350378862,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 24.9000040691
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "……貴方だってため息をついていたでしょう\nその様子だと、貴方もプレゼントを買いに来たのね",
      "startTime": 28.5673942567,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.7333340963
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "誰かさんに、ちゃんと用意しておけって釘を刺された\nからね。kanaにぴったりなものを選んだわよ。ほら",
      "startTime": 36.0000019073,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "へぇ、本を選んだのね。『どんな礼儀知らずでも\n読めば変われる、大人のマナー100選』……",
      "startTime": 46.6303043366,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50.4333329519
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "ベストセラーにもなったマナーの本なんだけど\nkanaにぴったりじゃない？",
      "startTime": 53.2271626442,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.2999980927
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "kanaってば、私達の方が年上なのに、態度悪いし\nケータリングの食べ方も汚いし、勉強が必要でしょ？",
      "startTime": 59.6251519203,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "それはそうだけど、貴方、本当にこれを渡すつもり？",
      "startTime": 63.6333342235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.6333342235
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 68.9333220165
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "何か問題でもあるの？",
      "startTime": 68.9333220165,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 70.9999917348
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "大ありよ。kanaにマナーがないって言ってるような\nものでしょう。それも、雑誌の編集部の人達の前で",
      "startTime": 74.2331600151,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.3999891917
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ？　別にいいじゃない、実際ないんだから\nこの前なんて椅子の上にあぐらかいてたし",
      "startTime": 83.2185724179,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.6666558583
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "実際にないからこそ、冗談じゃ済まなくなるのよ\nkanaには必要だとは思うけれど、危険過ぎるわ",
      "startTime": 91.1665973663,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.7666512807
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02-kor010.m4a",
      "text": "げー……もう買っちゃったのに……\nそういうmihoはなんにしたのよ",
      "startTime": 98.8333354949,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.5333179474
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "私は、体組成計にしたわ\n体脂肪率や筋肉量、基礎代謝量まで測れる優れものよ",
      "startTime": 104.3666751861,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 109.2666477203
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02-kor011.m4a",
      "text": "へー、いいじゃない\n健康オタクのmihoらしいわね",
      "startTime": 111.2333354949,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.5999800364
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "kanaは食っちゃ寝してばかりで、自己管理が甘いし\nぴったりでしょう。枕にしないことだけを願ってるわ",
      "startTime": 116.9666741688,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 121.266646703
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02-kor012.m4a",
      "text": "……それ、本人に言わないわよね？\n言わなくても気付かれそうだけど",
      "startTime": 124.6000021616,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.0999790191
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02-kor013.m4a",
      "text": "裏で暴れ狂ってるところを誰かに見られて\nリークでもされたら、洒落にならないんだけど",
      "startTime": 130.0051046423,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.3333052317
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "さすがにkanaでもそこまで暴れたりは……いえ……\nあの子なら、体組成計を壁に投げつけたりしそうね",
      "startTime": 139.2050644179,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 143.1332960764
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02-mhk010.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……プレゼント選びって面倒だわ\nとにかく、お互いもう少し探しましょう",
      "startTime": 147.6110200427,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 152.2
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 152.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02-kor014.m4a",
      "text": "っていうか、なんでぴったりなものを選んでるのに\nダメな訳？　ちゃんとkanaのこと考えてるでしょ",
      "startTime": 156.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 160.4999586741
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02-mhk011.m4a",
      "text": "一理あるわね。一番悪いのは、嫌味に見えるような\nものを選ばれる、kana自身の日頃の行いかしら",
      "startTime": 165.2000043232,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 169.2332889556
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02-kor015.m4a",
      "text": "まったくだわ。ねぇ、もうテキトーに決めちゃわない？\nkanaのために時間使うなんて、もったいないわよ",
      "startTime": 173.5666709899,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 176.7999434153
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02-mhk012.m4a",
      "text": "……そうね。正直、畳の目でも数えていた方がマシだわ\nあの子がほしそうなものを買って早く帰りましょう",
      "startTime": 182.9720859527,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 186.2999535877
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_02-kor016.m4a",
      "text": "誕生日が近いし、SNSにほしいもの書いてるんじゃ\nない？　目が腐りそうだけど、確認してみよっか",
      "startTime": 189.5442064777,
